# Kokomi - Minimal HTML generator from Markdown texts

## Installation

    $ cpanm .

## Required Modules

- Text::Xslate
- Text::Markdown
- Path::Class

## Usage

1. Make directories *tmpl*, *data*, *html*.
2. Make *header.tt* and *footer.tt* onto tmpl directory.
3. Write Markdown texts onto data directory.
4. Run *kokomi.pl*.
5. HTML is Generated.

